race.name: Bojangles' Southern 500
race.comments: Jeremy Clements won the Johnsonville 180 at Road America, his first victory in the NASCAR XFINITY Series. Prior to the start of the race, the No. 01 car dropped to the rear of the field for missing driver introductions.
